Name:                shady-render
Version:             0.6.1
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.6
Synopsis:            Functional GPU programming - rendering
Category:            Graphics, GPU
Description:
  Rendering of shaders generated by shady-gen, for GPU execution.
  See also shady-gen, shady-graphics, shady-tv, and shady-examples
  .
